### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AI - Correction de texte (LanguageTool)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Configuration (Dev)
@host = http://localhost:8080
@auth = {{host}}/api/auth
@api = {{host}}/api/ai

### ─── Login ───
POST {{auth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken); %}

### ─── Corriger un texte (francais) ───
POST {{api}}/correct
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "text": "je sui allee a la mer hier et jai manger du poisson",
  "language": "fr"
}

### ─── Corriger un texte (anglais) ───
POST {{api}}/correct
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "text": "I has went to the store yestarday and buyed some apples",
  "language": "en-US"
}

### ─── Texte sans faute ───
POST {{api}}/correct
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "text": "Bonjour, comment allez-vous aujourd'hui ?",
  "language": "fr"
}
